  "2333510": {
    "name": "刃裔学院",
    "steam_appid": 2333510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/670f0ead709f45abf7b7def2239d8fac.poster.avif?t=1769019785\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/670f0ead709f45abf7b7def2239d8fac.webm?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/670f0ead709f45abf7b7def2239d8fac.mp4?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>操控刃裔小队，让受过专业训练的战士们通过技能的合作打出威力十足的连击，击败敌人。<br><br>刃裔学院的学生们必须保护阿布吉塔利亚这座城市免受各种威胁，同时他们还得平衡学院里的社交生活。别忘了在战斗过后管理团队并鼓励成员们努力学习，避免战士们的人生堕入混沌之中！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/52339533f8d412ee5594c2b43bb9ec2d.poster.avif?t=1769019785\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/52339533f8d412ee5594c2b43bb9ec2d.webm?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/52339533f8d412ee5594c2b43bb9ec2d.mp4?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >暂停、拟定策略、执行</h2>使用刃裔学院「即时可暂停」的战斗系统，暂停时间并规划小队后续的行动，拟定出最佳的攻击顺序以打出完美连击。在战斗的过程中，操控团队成员们躲避敌人的法术和攻击，并对敌人施加持续的负面伤害，让战斗更持久。当然，你也可以灵活地利用周边环境，逆转局势，让敌人瞬间落入劣势。一切可能性操之在己！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/1d69f031b04b06f726f59c824781bcdf.poster.avif?t=1769019785\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/1d69f031b04b06f726f59c824781bcdf.webm?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/1d69f031b04b06f726f59c824781bcdf.mp4?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索刃裔学院</h2>这所学院供英雄们学习新技能，在战斗后休息、游玩。随着团队内新英雄的加入，成员们彼此相处增进感情，角色间的人际关系也会有所成长和发展。在踏上新任务之前，你将有机会提前获得有关阿布吉塔利亚最新状况的情报，为小队技能配置做好准备，以便发动新一波的攻势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/171c51c8f73d9dcf03c6d5d4dab1019c.poster.avif?t=1769019785\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/171c51c8f73d9dcf03c6d5d4dab1019c.webm?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333510/extras/171c51c8f73d9dcf03c6d5d4dab1019c.mp4?t=1769019785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造小队</h2>在冒险的旅途中，召集各路英雄组成团队。每位英雄都有自己独特的强项、弱点和背景故事。你可以了解这些英雄们在战斗中的表现，依照你的游戏风格调整小队的阵容，亦或是培养喜爱的英雄们之间的关系，增进彼此感情。打造属于你的独特团队，灵活地使用各个技能与连击，缔结黑暗契约，协助大家在这座阴影笼罩的城市中存活下来！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>即时可暂停</strong>：在战斗中，你可暂停时间规划下一步的攻击，智取敌人。<br></li><li><strong>连击系统</strong>：结合攻击与技能，打出强力连击。<br></li><li><strong>独特角色</strong>：为小队招募不同的英雄，每位英雄都有各自的强项、弱点及背景故事。<br></li><li><strong>人际关系</strong>：培养角色之间的感情，这将会影响到你任务的成败。<br></li><li><strong>契约</strong>：这种强力的仪式能够变更角色的能力与技能。<br></li><li><strong>天赋树</strong>：管理升级并解锁技能。逐步解锁越来越多的强力法术！<br></li><li><strong>高难度的首领战</strong>：对战独特首领。他们拥有着恐怖的力量，你必须精通战斗系统的运作机制才有办法与之抗敌。</li></ul>",
